These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, indonesian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, climbing
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, skateboard
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the indonesian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | indonesian    | malaysian |
| Sport         | climbing | cricket    |
| Transport     | bus     | skateboard      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea
There are 2 different nationalities: british, french
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the british is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | tea  | almond-milk   |
| Nationality   | french | british  |
| Transport     | trike   | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, skydiving
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, mystery
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, soccer
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | hiking   | skydiving  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | sports  |
| Sport         | snowboarding   | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
