.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: peach, orange
The people have 2 different jobs:  dressmaker, project-manager
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the dressmaker##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
3. the person eating peach is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | orange | peach     |
| Job     | project-manager | dressmaker |
| Sport   | parkour | handball    |

 #################################

 
