.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, card-games
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, german
2 different pets are kept: fish, goat
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the egyptian is on the left of the german##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | card-games | cooking |
| Nationality   | egyptian     | german     |
| Pet           | goat          | fish     |

